人接種；單日接種量比5間社區疫苗接種中心的接種總量多，形容市民反應踴躍。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">聶德權說，已經有心理準備，疫苗接種計劃繼續進行時，有個別市民會在接種後出現較嚴重的反應，甚至有死亡事件，強調會按同一原則處理每宗個案</span>，開誠布公向市民交代，承諾加強各方溝通和改善通報機制。 <br />\n<br />\n聶德權又指，昨日共有67名預約到社區疫苗接種中心打針的市民，經醫護評估後，認為不適宜接種，建議他們詢問醫生意見，或者稍後再預約接種。他認為，包括長者在內的接種人士，都很清楚掌握疫苗資訊，他們如有疑問，亦會詢問在場醫護，指現有安排是穩妥。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381475&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ac3a03d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381475</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"即係同你講打咗有機會死囉，不過係都唔認同支針有直接關係，吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25ae4174d64950bf198382d65178e2ff44c7471","tid":2431774,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"支持藍屍快啲去打，用身體下架科興疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8012316bf1bd32a898e2064b26894a7bb6b616","tid":2431774,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"你呢？"},{"pid":"e4586ced4eb06429aa282862fb37df1d1db5efe8","tid":2431774,"uid":281117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"越來越欣賞政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賠？賠乜L野呀？<br />\n隻疫苗咁新邊個保證到安全呀？<br />\n一早講L左啦！"},{"pid":"63cf6a340365e4a2dabb26331e74d0d3226358e8","tid":2431774,"uid":6964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e0519246335c045a94d44364b120a2af0987c1a","tid":2431774,"uid":20170,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:38:11.000Z","msg":"嗰二百幾萬真係吊喺驢仔前面嘅蘿蔔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci